<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Rappel renouvellement — EnMémoire.com</title></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#F4F6F9;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;">
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding:32px 16px;">
<tr><td align="center">
<table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
       style="background:white;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(27,43,75,.1);overflow:hidden;max-width:560px;width:100%;">

  <tr><td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B2B4B,#2C4270);padding:28px 32px;text-align:center;">
    <h1 style="color:white;font-weight:300;font-size:22px;margin:0;">
      ⏰ <span style="color:#C9A84C;">En</span>Mémoire<span style="color:#C9A84C;">.com</span>
    </h1>
  </td></tr>

  <tr><td style="padding:32px;">
    <h2 style="color:#1B2B4B;font-size:20px;font-weight:400;margin:0 0 12px;">
      Votre page expire dans <span style="color:#C9A84C;">{{ days }} jour{{ days > 1 ? 's' : '' }}</span>
    </h2>

    <p style="color:#6B7280;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 20px;">
      Bonjour <strong style="color:#1B2B4B;">{{ owner.firstName }}</strong>,
      la page mémorielle de <strong style="color:#1B2B4B;">{{ page.deceasedFullName }}</strong>
      expire le <strong style="color:#1B2B4B;">{{ expires_at|date('d/m/Y') }}</strong>.
    </p>

    <div style="background:#FEF3C7;border-left:4px solid #F59E0B;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:.875rem;color:#92400E;">
        ⚠️ Après expiration, la page ne sera plus accessible au public. Renouvelez maintenant pour éviter toute interruption.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="{{ renewal_url }}"
         style="display:inline-block;background:#C9A84C;color:#1B2B4B;text-decoration:none;
                padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">
        🔄 Renouveler maintenant
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size:.78rem;color:#9CA3AF;text-align:center;margin:20px 0 0;">
      Vous recevez cet email car vous êtes propriétaire de la page de {{ page.deceasedFullName }}.
    </p>
  </td></tr>

  <tr><td style="background:#F8F4EE;border-top:1px solid #E8E0D4;padding:14px 32px;text-align:center;">
    <p style="color:#9CA3AF;font-size:12px;margin:0;">© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} EnMémoire.com</p>
  </td></tr>

</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
